00:05:50,864 --> 00:05:53,492
<i>Mr. David Frost!</i>

107
00:05:53,667 --> 00:05:54,691
(CHUCKLES)

108
00:05:54,768 --> 00:05:57,362
Thank you, thank you.

109
00:05:59,172 --> 00:06:00,764
Hello. Good evening.

110
00:06:00,840 --> 00:06:03,968
And with the eyes of the world
focused on the White House,

111
00:06:04,044 --> 00:06:06,672
here in Australia,
burglars have broken into

112
00:06:06,746 --> 00:06:09,078
a meat factory in Brisbane

113
