00:39:31,482 --> 00:39:33,746
This guy wiretapped
17 people.

754
00:39:33,818 --> 00:39:34,876
BIRT: Seventeen?

755
00:39:34,952 --> 00:39:35,976
Including his own brother.

756
00:39:36,054 --> 00:39:37,954
But you know what?
We can't ask him
about his brother,

757
00:39:38,022 --> 00:39:40,820
'cause frankly,
if Donald Nixon
was my brother,

