00:40:18,996 --> 00:40:20,588
Are they going to
give us the money?

774
00:40:20,665 --> 00:40:22,189
How serious are they?

775
00:40:22,266 --> 00:40:25,758
You have to set up that
he has an anti-democratic
personality.

776
00:40:25,837 --> 00:40:27,498
There's a reason they
call him Tricky Dick.

777
00:40:27,572 --> 00:40:31,099
Because I had written about
and watched Nixon for years,

778
00:40:31,175 --> 00:40:33,302
I got to play him
in our rehearsals.

779
00:40:33,377 --> 00:40:35,436
<i>You know,</i>
<i>the fellas would</i>
<i>throw me a question,</i>

780
00:40:35,513 --> 00:40:38,414
<i>and I would try and anticipate</i>
<i>what his response might be.</i>

781
00:40:38,483 --> 00:40:40,508
BIRT: Okay,
the White House
taping system.

