805
00:41:49,720 --> 00:41:51,381
"to help him
with the research.

806
00:41:51,455 --> 00:41:54,686
"Clearly
the famous TV interviewer
will pull no punches."

807
00:41:54,759 --> 00:41:56,192
"Crack investigators"?

808
00:41:56,260 --> 00:41:57,318
Can I be Crack One?

809
00:41:57,395 --> 00:41:58,862
Can I be Deep Crack?

810
00:42:01,032 --> 00:42:02,897
David, can I talk
to you for a sec?

811
00:42:02,967 --> 00:42:04,366
After researching
my last book,

