00:42:38,135 --> 00:42:40,035
He'll be right
with you. Yeah.

831
00:42:43,274 --> 00:42:44,866
Jack.
<i>Watergate.</i>

832
00:42:44,942 --> 00:42:46,034
Yes, Jack.

833
00:42:46,110 --> 00:42:49,705
Our lawyers want us to agree
